  "id": "parallax-layers",
  "title": "Parallax Layers",
  "summary": "Background layers scroll slower than foreground content for a depth illusion — pure CSS.",
  "description": "Uses CSS 3D transforms (perspective + translateZ + scale) on a scroll container so deeper layers move slower, achieving parallax without JS scroll listeners.",
